{"lemma":"سَحاب","slug":"سَحاب","root":"س.ح.ب","root_slug":"س-ح-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/س-ح-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun_prop","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"سَحاب","root":"سحب","pos":"N","occurrence_count":9},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n19038"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B3%D9%8E%D8%AD%D8%A7%D8%A8"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"clouds","tags":["collective"],"examples":[{"text":"هُوَ الَّذِي يُرِيكُمُ الْبَرْقَ خَوْفًا وَطَمَعًا وَيُنْشِئُ السَّحَابَ الثِّقَالَ"},{"text":"وَتَرَى الْجِبَالَ تَحْسَبُهَا جَامِدَةً وَهِيَ تَمُرُّ مَرَّ السَّحَابِ صُنْعَ اللَّهِ الَّذِي أَتْقَنَ كُلَّ شَيْءٍ إِنَّهُ خَبِيرٌ بِمَا تَفْعَلُونَ"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"zip fastener"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From the root س ح ب (s ḥ b)"},"ipa":["/sa.ħaːb/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n19038","headword_ar":"سَحَابٌ","root":"sHb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[termed in the S and K pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saHaAbapN","text_ar":"سَحَابَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suHubN","text_ar":"سُحُبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saHaAy^ibu","text_ar":"سَحَايِبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] is, accord. to As, [correctly,] a coll. gen. n., used alike as masc. and fem. and sing. and pl.; (MF, TA;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saHaAbapN","text_ar":"سَحَابَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is its n. un.; (MF, Msb, * TA;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suHubN","text_ar":"سُحُبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saHaAbN","text_ar":"سَحَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saHaAbapN","text_ar":"سَحَابَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (L, Msb, * MF, TA;) it may be pl. of either of these; (L, MF, TA;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saHaAy^ibu","text_ar":"سَحَايِبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saHaAbapN","text_ar":"سَحَابَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"absolutely, and of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saHaAbN","text_ar":"سَحَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"when used as fem.: (MF, TA:) it signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Clouds"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a collection of clouds"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (S, K, KL, TA, &c.;) and ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"clouds"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from which the rain comes:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) so called because drawn along in the air; (Msb, TA;) or because they draw along one another; or because the winds draw them along; (TA;) or because they draw along their fringes. (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hbw","text_ar":"حبو"},{"kind":"text","text":".) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maTaratohumu","text_ar":"مَطَرَتْهُمُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Als~aHaAbapu","text_ar":"السَّحَابَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The cloud rained upon them"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aqamotu Einodahu saHaAbapa nahaAriY","text_ar":"اَقَمْتُ عِنْدَهُ سَحَابَةَ نَهَارِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I remained at his abode the whole of my day:"},{"kind":"text","text":"originally said in relation to a cloudy day; and then proverbially used in relation to any day. (A, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA zilotu A^afoEaluhu saHaAbapa yawomiY","text_ar":"مَا زِلْتُ اَفْعَلُهُ سَحَابَةَ يَوْمِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I ceased not to do it the whole of my day."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA='u","text_ar":"مَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Als~aHaAbi","text_ar":"السَّحَابِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[properly"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The water of the clouds"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is a term for (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wine."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jfn","text_ar":"جفن"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Als~aHaAbu","text_ar":"السَّحَابُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a name of (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The Prophet's turban;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, TA:) it was thus called as being likened to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sHAb","text_ar":"سحاب"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the rain because of its being drawn along in the air. (TA.) ―         -b5-  Also the name of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A sword of Dirar Ibn-El-Khattáb."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)"}],"source_refs":["MF","TA","Mgh"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}